      <title>Causes Of Panic Attacks Discussed Here</title>
      <link>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stop_anxiety/causes-of-panic-attacks-discussed-here/</link>
      <comments>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stop_anxiety/causes-of-panic-attacks-discussed-here/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Oct 2010 21:07:23 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Stop Anxiety Stop Panic</dc:creator>
