      <title>How to Control a Panic Attack – Stopping the Fear of Having a Panic Attack</title>
      <link>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stop_anxiety/how-to-control-a-panic-attack-stopping-the-fear-of-having-a-panic-attack/</link>
