      <title>Anxiety Without Medication – #1 Alternative For Treating Anxiety And Panic Attacks</title>
      <link>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stopping_panic/anxiety-without-medication-1-alternative-for-treating-anxiety-and-panic-attacks/</link>
      <comments>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stopping_panic/anxiety-without-medication-1-alternative-for-treating-anxiety-and-panic-attacks/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Aug 2010 22:43:41 +0000</pubDate>
      <dc:creator>Stop Anxiety Stop Panic</dc:creator>
