      <title>Easy and Effective Tips to End Panic Attacks</title>
      <link>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stopping_panic/easy-and-effective-tips-to-end-panic-attacks/</link>
      <comments>http://www.stopanxietystoppanic.com/stopping_panic/easy-and-effective-tips-to-end-panic-attacks/#comments</comments>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Aug 2010 12:02:01 +0000</pubDate>
